 top-tier games on broadcast networks to go head-to-head with TNT=E2=80=99s=
 schedule: Texans-Chiefs on NBC and Steelers-Ravens on Fox. You don=E2=80=
=99t need to wait for the Nielsen numbers to know that these games will dep=
lete the CFP viewership.</p>
